  files/devfsd-1.3.25-no-nis.patch:
  added patch to allow uclibc to compile without nis

  12 May 2004; Alexander Gabert <pappy@gentoo.org> devfsd-1.3.25-r6.ebuild,
  devfsd-1.3.25-r7.ebuild:
